---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Find an Aviation Medical Examiner (Template Preview) | Flight School Friend"
  description="This page will help future pilots understand how to research aviation medical examiners and what to clarify before training."
>
  <section class="bg-white max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest border border-slate-200">Template Preview</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Find an Aviation Medical Examiner</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">This page will help future pilots understand how to research aviation medical examiners and what to clarify before training.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What this page will eventually help compare:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-slate-600 space-y-1">
          <li>AME location & Medical certificate class</li>
          <li>FAA listing status</li>
          <li>Consultation availability</li>
          <li>Experience with complex cases</li>
          <li>Scheduling availability</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What to verify:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
            <li>Current FAA AME status</li>
            <li>Which certificate class you need</li>
            <li>Whether you should consult before submitting MedXPress</li>
            <li>Any medical history that may require documentation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 border-amber-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Questions to ask:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-amber-900 space-y-1 font-medium">
            <li>Do I need a consultation before a formal exam?</li>
            <li>Which class of medical should I pursue for my goal?</li>
            <li>Are there records I should gather first?</li>
            <li>Should I delay MedXPress until I understand my situation?</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/find/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">&larr; Back to Find</a>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">Start Here</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
